      <title>即使欧盟批准征收关税，中欧电动汽车谈判仍将继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/eu-china-ev-talks-to-continue-even-if-bloc-approves-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，即使成员国未来几天投票对电动汽车征税，欧盟和中国仍将继续谈判，寻找关税的替代解决方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/eu-china-ev-talks-to-continue-even-if-bloc-approves-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:41:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯预算显示普京的承诺价值 4000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/russian-budget-shows-400-billion-price-tag-for-putin-s-promises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据俄罗斯财政部称，俄罗斯计划在六年内投入超过 40 万亿卢布（4310 亿美元）来实现弗拉基米尔·普京在新总统任期内设定的社会目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/russian-budget-shows-400-billion-price-tag-for-putin-s-promises</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:36:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多力争与拜登一同禁止中国制造的汽车软件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/trudeau-aims-to-match-biden-on-banning-chinese-made-car-software</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰 (Chrystia Freeland) 周二表示，继美国采取类似举措后，加拿大也在考虑禁止在汽车上使用中国制造的软件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/trudeau-aims-to-match-biden-on-banning-chinese-made-car-software</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诈骗者冒充政治活动家，利用党派分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/scammers-pose-as-political-activists-to-play-on-partisan-divide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新研究表明，黑客正在利用美国的党派分歧来诱骗美国人点击网络钓鱼电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/scammers-pose-as-political-activists-to-play-on-partisan-divide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:17:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约大都会交通管理局警告不要借入超过 130 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/ny-s-mta-warns-against-borrowing-more-than-13-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最大的公共交通系统未来五年应该承担多少债务？纽约大都会运输署称 130 亿美元刚刚好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/ny-s-mta-warns-against-borrowing-more-than-13-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMLO 在墨西哥担任领导人的最后一周夺取了美国拥有的港口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/mexico-s-amlo-finalizes-expropriation-of-vulcan-vmc-port-quarry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥最终确定了控制其加勒比海岸 Vulcan Materials Co. 旗下港口和采石场的计划，这在该国总统离任前几天加剧了紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/mexico-s-amlo-finalizes-expropriation-of-vulcan-vmc-port-quarry</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 14:53:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基称俄罗斯炸弹袭击导致哈尔科夫三人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/russian-glide-bomb-attack-kills-three-in-kharkhiv-governor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，俄罗斯对乌克兰第二大城市的民用基础设施发动的袭击造成至少三人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/russian-glide-bomb-attack-kills-three-in-kharkhiv-governor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:57:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会敦促增加对美国劳工调查的资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/friends-of-bls-urge-congress-to-lift-funding-for-us-labor-survey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由前劳工统计局官员领导的团体正在敦促国会为该机构额外提供 2000 万美元，以支持一项他们所说的“预算危机”的关键劳动力市场调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/friends-of-bls-urge-congress-to-lift-funding-for-us-labor-survey</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在最后一次联合国演讲中敦促各国领导人支持联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/biden-s-final-un-speech-to-tout-alliances-even-as-conflicts-brew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在联合国大会的最后一次讲话中为其建立联盟应对全球挑战的努力进行了辩护，并敦促盟友继续这项工作，尽管乌克兰和中东的冲突给联盟带来了新的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/biden-s-final-un-speech-to-tout-alliances-even-as-conflicts-brew</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
